{"tid":923943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反公屋班垃圾五毛狗,屌晒你哋老母","createTime":"2018-12-01T16:40:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T04:13:46.000Z","uid":48234,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a575fe78f43d52ce5cff86e0561952b647f9611b","tid":923943,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T16:40:34.000Z","msg":"好呀,咁撚唔鍾意公屋,要拆撚晒佢呀嗎?冇問題<br />\n政府唔會俾香港搞撚到人人瞓街嘅,咁咪全港租金管制囉<br />\n限制住宅租金完全等於現時嘅公屋租金,唔超免稅,每多1蚊就扣1蚊稅<br />\n到時你班垃圾五毛狗害死全香港業主咋,仲要樓價跟住跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3bf5b0b7c2871042012aeb37ec81936e55754e2","tid":923943,"uid":209516,"like":8,"dislike":8,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a575fe78f43d52ce5cff86e0561952b647f9611b","tid":923943,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T16:40:34.000Z","msg":"好呀,咁撚唔鍾意公屋,要拆撚晒佢呀嗎?冇問題<br />\n政府唔會俾香港搞撚到人人瞓街嘅,咁咪全港租金管制囉<br />\n限制住宅租金完全等於現時嘅公屋租金,唔超免稅,每多1蚊就扣1蚊稅<br />\n到時你班垃圾五毛狗害死全香港業主咋,仲要樓價跟住跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T16:47:33.000Z","msg":"第一次見人窮得如此自豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"740cdb45cd8af2ec5364ba2d0b9e2005da37acc9","tid":923943,"uid":77222,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T16:58:13.000Z","msg":"樓主公屋仔？"},{"pid":"447afd845fff9aa3906663088b221344c5511c41","tid":923943,"uid":48234,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b3bf5b0b7c2871042012aeb37ec81936e55754e2","tid":923943,"uid":209516,"like":8,"dislike":8,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a575fe78f43d52ce5cff86e0561952b647f9611b","tid":923943,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"re